

Goal is to test interests/audiences with angles 
(ads following AID format then can iterate on ads later when ads testing)
 so can find out which angle resonates with which audience
(3 angles/ads ) (20$per adset) (with winning audiences begin testing ads, see notes)

Angles
-Your diet doesn't have to be unhealthy or difficult....
-Diets when done right can work wonders for your health, body and energy
-Tried a diet, but it didn't work? We think we can help you...

Messaging:
-focus on frustrations with previous diets and how the mediterranean diet and our 
solution solves these
(see lead)

Audiences list:
-broad interests
-male only
-female only

1. 

Angle/1st line:
Your diet doesn't have to be unhealthy or difficult...

Copy first 2 lines:

We know a way to make your diet healthy easy and consistent so you can enjoy the benefits of good health, lower fat and increased energy all the time.

You might have tried a "Diet Plan" in the past but it didn't work or if it did
it only worked for a while

Headline:
We need your help to help you

Body:
(lead on from lead to solution (see CPBs))

The problem is not you, it was probably the diet.

It might have been too restrictive and not complete

And eventually you couldn't follow it consistently.

Because it was not a fun diet.

Now, if we told you there was a way, a diet that was healthy, complete and 
easy would you be interested?

If you're reading this you must be.

The diet we're talking about is the mediterranean diet.

You may have heard of it or it might be completely new to you.

We're currently working on a way to bring this diet to you in a way that's practical and easy.

If you'd like to help us create this, answer a few questions


Creative:
-unhealthy diet


